snippet.title: Necesse Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The main trailer for Necesse version 0.21.
Necesse is available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1169040/Necesse/
Join the Discord server: https://discord.gg/FAFgrKD

Necesse is a top-down sandbox action-adventure game in a procedurally generated world. Progress your character's gear and settlement through fighting, mining, exploring, crafting, trading and more! 

Music by nosoapradio.us.
